Title: 9:00 A.M.-10:00 A.M.
Plot:
Teri manages to call CTU using a stolen cell phone. She and Jack have an emotional conversation, but her signal dies before the call can be traced.

Nina and Tony find themselves facing a new boss, Alberta Green, as they continue to secretly help Jack.

Palmer's political associates begin to sweat as Carl plans to take serious action against Keith's therapist.

Jack uncovers a new name from the key card that may lead him to Gaines.
GuestStars: Currie Graham,  Ivar Brogger,  Tracy E. Wilson,  Desmond Bull,  Martin Morales,  Manny Perry,  Maurice Dunster,  Burke Stuart
